snippet: A hospital spokeswoman says Olympic star Amy Van Dyken Rouen is in good condition despite her spinal injury.
abstract: Swimmer Amy Van Dyken Rouen, six-time Olympic gold medalist, severs her spine in an all-terrain vehicle accident.
lead_paragraph: A hospital spokeswoman says Olympic star Amy Van Dyken Rouen is in good condition despite her spinal injury.

headline.main: Six-Time Gold Medalist Severs Spine in Accident
